languages.text: {n}Вероятнее всего, этот человек принадлежит к редкой породе псайкеров — биомантам. Они могут исцелять себя от самых безнадежных ран и болезней.{/n}
{n}This man appears to belong to a rare variety of psykers — biomancers capable of recovering even from otherwise deadly wounds and diseases.{/n}

{n}Those blessed with affluence in the Imperium are known to make use of rejuvenat treatments, but not this man. He appears to belong to a rare variety of psykers — biomancers capable of controlling the energies within their own body and thus sustaining themselves for hundreds of years.{/n}
